
🔷 Project 3 — Disney Social Media Lakehouse (diagrame)


[Twitter API]   [TikTok API]   [Social Feeds]
        │             │              │
        └─────────────┴──────────────┘
                     │
          [Azure Data Factory]
       (API Ingestion + Scheduling)
                     │
                     ▼
        [Snowflake - Raw Stage]
     (JSON / CSV - Unprocessed Data)
                     │
                     ▼
        [Databricks - PySpark]
   - JSON Flattening
   - Data Enrichment
   - Deduplication
                     │
                     ▼
              [dbt Layer]
   - Transformation Models
   - Schema Validation Tests
   - Data Quality Checks
                     │
                     ▼
         [Snowflake Warehouse]
   - Fact: Engagement, Impressions
   - Dim: Campaign, User
   - Clustering (timestamp, campaign_id)
                     │
                     ▼
             [Power BI]
   - Campaign ROI Dashboard
   - Trend Analysis

