[ERP]   [CRM]   [Banking APIs]
   │       │         │
   └───────┴─────────┘
           │
   ┌───────────────┐
   │ Ingestion     │
   │ ADF (Batch)   │
   │ Kafka (Stream)│
   └───────────────┘
           │
           ▼
   [Azure Data Lake Gen2]
   - Raw Layer
   - Processed Layer
   - Curated Layer
           │
           ▼
   [Databricks]
   - ETL Pipelines
   - Streaming Processing
           │
           ▼
   [Synapse Analytics]
   - Financial Models
   - Reporting Tables

   🔐 Governance Layer (Overlay)
   - Data Lineage
   - RBAC
   - PII Masking

           ▼
   [BI / Finance Dashboards]

